      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained premium SUV that perfectly balances luxury and utility. This vehicle is in solid, reliable condition and has been a smoke-free, family-owned car since new. The exterior displays a deep luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains refined; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the heated seats to the high-fidelity sound system and navigation, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent full synthetic oil change and a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires installed last season. The engine pulls strongly with a smooth, quiet idle, and the transmission shifts through all gears with precision. This is a turn-key vehicle that offers a premium driving experience and long-term reliability for its next owner. Full service history documentation is available for review.",
